OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry throughout the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Clear skies at first, but
OL,8,Fhigh cloud spreading in from the west
OL,9,Flater. Chance of some patchy overnight
OL,10,Ffrost developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start it will
OL,13,Fbe another dry and bright day with
OL,14,Fgood prolonged sunny spells and
OL,15,Ffeeling a bit milder again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
